Based on the metric analysis (orders cpu and orders latency-90 both showing consecutive, large breaches of their global P95 starting at 2024-01-19T16:16:00Z) and the lack of error-log/trace evidence, the most likely root cause is a performance fault in the orders service caused by high CPU usage.

